2026-05-13T17:23:31.6086149Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-13T17:23:31.6086475Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-13T17:23:31.6087179Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
